# Generated dense i18n resolved tables. These directories STAY committed (they are
# the tsc safety net + the runtime read source), but each is a large machine-emitted
# artifact regenerated by `npm run i18n:build` / `npm run i18n:admin`. Marking them
# `linguist-generated` makes GitHub collapse them in pull-request diffs and excludes
# them from language statistics. Display hygiene only - not removal, not gitignore.
src/ui/i18n.resolved.generated/** linguist-generated
src/admin/i18n.resolved.generated/** linguist-generated
